column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, s.class, s.z as redshift, petroR5#_r, st.logmass FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyNoDust AS st ON p.ra = st.ra AND p.dec = st.dec WHERE p.u BETWEEN # AND # AND g BETWEEN # AND # AND s.class = GALAXY
